source.name: Greenhouse Gas Emissions From Fuel Combustion, By Fuel Type, Million Metric Tons
source.description: The Greenhouse Gas Emissions Inventory details the estimated New York State emissions releases from fuel combustion.  The dataset includes a fuel type breakdown, by sector, for the current year.
